- Develop and manage relationships with alumni, employers of VGU's graduates in the database of alumni surveys and develop new partnership, new companies and organizations;
- Coordinate to develop the online job portal of VGU. Update and answer daily the requests on online job portal when the portal is available;
- Organize events/courses to help students developing career-related skills and experience, to prepare students for the job market;
